attributes.action: Fund and support an infertility and mental health awareness campaign
attributes.additional_details:
My aim is to get help and support for those suffering, build a webpage with guidance for those that need it and provide a nationwide service, so please helps us help them.

We already have a facebook group, ivf food & health. This helps with diet and mental help supporting each other.
attributes.background: I have first hand experience of infertility struggles and i want to help others and raise awareness of mental health problems associated with infertility.
